33
00:02:40.950 --> 00:02:44.283
DR. HARROW: Is that why you keep starting
imaginary fights in our hospital?

34
00:02:44.366 --> 00:02:45.616
No, you're not a doctor.

35
00:02:46.950 --> 00:02:50.200
Look. I feel real.
I feel like a real doctor.

36
