or a library.

63
00:04:12.366 --> 00:04:14.158
Or a... psych ward?

64
00:04:15.991 --> 00:04:22.366
Yeah. Or it could be.
Could be a psych ward. Yeah.

65
00:04:22.450 --> 00:04:29.033
What I find extremely interesting
is this new... The new animal character.

66
00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:30.408
Um...

67
00:04:30.866 --> 00:04:33.991
- Hippopotamus?
- I find that really interesting.

68
00:04:34.533 --> 00:04:38.241
This hippo could break down the walls
between you and Steven,

69
00:04:38.325 --> 00:04:40.283
and we might finally understand.

70
00:04:42.825 --> 00:04:43.908
Understand what?

71
00:04:44.366 --> 00:04:49.116
